metadata.description:
The work is dedicated to Ukrainian units that protect the civilized world from destruction and maintain peace in Europe. The funds will go to support the Ukrainian army.

I dedicate the NFT to the 93rd Brigade "Kholodnyi Yar", these fighters know no fatigue and snatch victory with their tenacious paws, like the eagle on their patch.
